    "To handle the complexity, we propose to tackle the problem by splitting it into two sub-problems: (1) client-DNN mapping and (2) DNN selection.",
    "We optimize each sub-problem iteratively to improve the overall accuracy objective without violating the latency SLO constraint.",
    "We first discuss the client-DNN mapping problem, which later serves as a building block for the DNN selection problem.",
    "The goal is to map the set of clients to a given set of DNN instances, optimizing the overall accuracy as defined in Eq.",
    "Our client-DNN mapping algorithm is based on the key observation that the overall accuracy is maximized when the larger DNNs (more accurate ones) are assigned with higher aggregate request rates."
